name: Inferno Maw Chiller
text: In a realm of twilight magics, the village called it Scorchgut, a living icebox with a fiery heart. It engulfed feasts whole with ravenous delight, belching frost and flame. Whispers told of curses old and arcane hungers unsated. Yet, in winter's deepest scorn, Scorchgut's warmth was a peculiar solace.
